###------- Livros-----------------------

### Lista livros
GET {{baseUrl}}/books
Content-Type: application/json
x-auth-token:{{token}}

### Busca livro por ID
GET {{baseUrl}}/books/{{bookId}}
Content-Type: application/json

### Adicionar um livro
POST {{baseUrl}}/books
Content-Type: application/json
x-auth-token:{{token}}

{
  "googleBookId": "g0s_T_9HlOKC",
  "status": "reading"
}

### Buscar um livro pelo ID
PUT {{baseUrl}}/books/{{bookId}}
Content-Type: application/json
x-auth-token: {{token}}

{
  "status": "read"
}

### Deletar livro
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/books/{{bookId}}
Content-Type: application/json
x-auth-token:{{token}}

### Pesquisa livro na API do Google Livros
GET  {{baseUrl}}/books/search?q=clean code
Content-Type: application/json

###----Notas----
### Adicionar nota ao livro
POST {{baseUrl}}/book-notes/{{bookId}}/notes
Content-Type: application/json
x-auth-token:{{token}}

{
  "text": "Minha nota sobre este livro."
}

### Listar notas do livro
GET {{baseUrl}}/book-notes/{{bookId}}/notes
Content-Type: application/json
x-auth-token:{{token}}

### Remover nota do livro
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/book-notes/{{bookId}}/notes/{{noteId}}
Content-Type: application/json
x-auth-token:{{token}}

###----Reviews----
### Adicionar avaliação ao livro
